      "writtenOn": "2018-10-31T21:46:29Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Done\n\nSeems like this is also the assumption made between the CPU context and the minidump context: https://chromium.googlesource.com/crashpad/crashpad/+/master/snapshot/minidump/thread_snapshot_minidump.cc#243",
      "parentUuid": "fa4a4902_d9995634",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 58,
        "startChar": 2,
